{"tid":388343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【CUHK】操普通話學生打算撕毀民主牆上的港獨單張被阻止","createTime":"2017-09-05T11:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T13:44:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":275,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f662041c97844b5db3236fe503eadfb656fff899","tid":388343,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"【學苑即時】19:04 中大文化廣場有學生打算撕毀民主牆上的港獨單張，但被在場人士阻止。該名學生先以普通話，其後轉用英文與中大學生會外務副會長朱安妮理論，稱自己有權拆除民主牆上的單張，又質疑學生會無權管理民主牆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p350x350/21370939_2170141849666193_6944495350202562109_n.jpg?oh=2490263a0ae076e0a3a9254666c8c6dd&amp;oe=5A22F523\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp350x350%2F21370939_2170141849666193_6944495350202562109_n.jpg%3Foh%3D2490263a0ae076e0a3a9254666c8c6dd%26oe%3D5A22F523&h=6b0ac493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21369460_2170142196332825_209592137369273412_n.jpg?oh=9fd2969ce651828eb4d9f11cdb0bf9dd&amp;oe=5A2077D8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21369460_2170142196332825_209592137369273412_n.jpg%3Foh%3D9fd2969ce651828eb4d9f11cdb0bf9dd%26oe%3D5A2077D8&h=a82af4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fundergradnews%2F&d=z0qExKJve019zTluS%2Ft0s5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6330771b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/</a>"},{"pid":"64be552287dc069abe167c70e530ef58c1fe5bff","tid":388343,"uid":427,"like":381,"dislike":3,"score":378,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"臭大陸閪"},{"pid":"54bfe13ae018f083a9690b209d0ed5097e81be1c","tid":388343,"uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"雖遠必撕"},{